<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stubborn-adj">stubborn <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'stʌbən/    美 /'stʌbərn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>倔强的；顽强的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She can be really stubborn.
她有时相当固执。</p><footer>人教① – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was stubborn and overcame all the difficulties.
她很顽强，克服了所有困难。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-tough">2.<strong>难对付的；棘手的 (tough)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>stubborn stains / illnesses
顽渍/疾</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>stubborn problems
棘手的问题</p></div></div>